reviewText: IWA and CZW.What's not to like. If your a fan of classic Cactus Jack death matches you'll love these. Blood,glass,fire,tacks. It's the death match!!!!!!!!!!!!!

I do not have this box set but I do have all three volumes and they all deliver so for the price it is more then worth it. I like vol 2 the best which feature matches from CZW and goes over 3 hours and is worth the purchase  price alone.
